title: Magnetic Island Bay Dayz Festival has something for everyone!Travelandtourworld.com
text:
Magnetic Island Bay Dayz Festival has something for everyone! Published on : Monday, September 21, 2015
During the month-long Magnetic Island Bay Dayz Festival each September, Magnetic Island in Queensland bursts with 50+ events and activities.
The program includes island-wide competitions, the Rotary Beer Can Regatta, Morleys Spring Equinox Fair, one-off cultural events, Talk Like A Pirate Day, Movies Under The Stars, Mega Markets, the very popular Sand Sculpture Competition and Oktoberfest which is set right on picturesque Horseshoe Bay beach.
Each of the four main bays and beaches on the island has events over the month till October 4.
There are also outdoor movies, live music, art exhibitions, gallery openings, environmental walks and talks, workshops, restaurant discounts, health and beauty discounts â€“ you name it, the Festival has something for everyone!
